The share of legal weapons in crime is very low
The Russian Ministry of the Interior is planning to tighten up the arms law for private arms owners.
The authorities are thus responding to recent events: injured in the shooting of weddings and seven dead in the amoclop of the Moscow lawyer Dmitri Winogradow.
