What do you think is going to happen in less than a month?
This is one of those disaster reports that we people are so happy to jump on.
With our band The Tap Tap we make fun of it and say that we are the only band in the world that can collect enough positive energy to stop or prevent the world's decline.
In December, you will also realize a unique project with three concerts against the world's downfall.
